      "memo": "Enterprise RAG demands articulable compliance and audit trails, but ultimately validates through retrieval accuracy and output quality.",
      "detail": "Regulated enterprises require documented data governance, access controls, and audit trails for RAG deployments. These process requirements coexist with outcome-based acceptance: the system must actually retrieve accurately and generate useful answers. Compliance documentation alone does not validate a RAG system that returns wrong results. The hybrid basis reflects enterprise reality where both process and outcome must satisfy different stakeholders."
    }
  }
}
